74
00:03:11,810 --> 00:03:12,670
Are you drunk?

75
00:03:12,970 --> 00:03:14,670
No. It's Chinese New Year.
We should be happy.

76
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:16,780
Yes, we're so happy.

77
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:18,810
Big cousin,

78
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:20,410
Sister Tang and you

79
00:03:20,410 --> 00:03:21,370
have grown up

80
00:03:21,370 --> 00:03:22,250
got a job.

81
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,460
Why are you still sitting with the kids?

82
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,160
I...

83
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,510
No matter how old you are,

84
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:28,760
as long as you're not married,

85
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,300
you're always children

86
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,390
in this village.

87
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,180
Yes, that's right.

88
00:03:34,010 --> 00:03:36,370
Our family has the same rule.

89
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:37,460
As long as you're not married,

90
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:39,670
