92
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,740
so that maybe we can

93
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,460
sit with the adults next year, okay?

94
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:48,110
Are you silly?

95
00:03:48,410 --> 00:03:50,040
Didn't you hear it?

96
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,020
If you're not married,
you can still get red envelopes

97
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,670
every year.

98
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:54,850
That's right.

99
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:56,720
- Yes.
- Maybe I shouldn't grow up.

100
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,370
Besides, isn't it nice to sit with kids?

101
00:03:58,370 --> 00:03:59,710
Those seniors always ask too much.

102
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:01,460
- Come on.
- Come on.

103
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,970
Ms. Zhou,

104
00:04:02,970 --> 00:04:03,950
I want to make a toast

105
00:04:04,090 --> 00:04:05,970
to you and Mr. Tang.

106
00:04:05,970 --> 00:04:06,950
Why?

107
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,200
Because Jiang Shiyan is so lucky

108
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,510
to have met Tang.

109
00:04:11,010 --> 00:04:12,150
In high school,

110
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,720
Tang

111
00:04:13,850 --> 00:04:15,620
helped Jiang Shiyan
to improve his grades

112
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:17,320
from around 400 points

113
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:19,270
to over 600 points!

114
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:22,020
Fangping said this before.

115
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,050
She said

116
00:04:23,050 --> 00:04:24,760
Jiang Shiyan might not

117
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:25,810
get into a college.

118
00:04:25,810 --> 00:04:27,270
If it really had happened,

119
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:29,950
he could only help her sell seafood.

120
00:04:30,730 --> 00:04:32,050
- But I didn't expect...
- You never thought

121
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:33,580
I'd sell seafood now,

122
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:35,960
but on online platforms.

123
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,850
Apart from seafood,

124
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:39,170
I also sell tofu, sausages, chili sauce,

125
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:40,190
and stinky rice noodles.

126
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,930
Shiyan is so capable.

127
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:44,210
(Leisure House)
Let's wish the elderly

128
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:45,050
longevity,

129
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:46,400
and the kids good health!

130
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,240
Cheers!

131
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,490
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

132
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,330
Happy Chinese New Year!

133
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:51,370
Happy Chinese New Year!

134
00:04:51,370 --> 00:04:52,900
Happy Chinese New Year, sweetheart.

135
00:05:16,490 --> 00:05:17,440
My mother always asks me

136
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,200
to learn from Sister Tang.

137
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,360
She said

138
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,640
she ranked first in every academic year.

139
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,840
Last time,

140
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:23,770
Aunt gave me

141
00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:24,810
Sister Tang's textbooks.

142
00:05:24,810 --> 00:05:25,950
I opened it

143
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,640
only to find it

144
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:31,050
full of orderly notes and remarks.

145
00:05:31,050 --> 00:05:32,530
- It's not like that.
- Exactly.

146
00:05:32,530 --> 00:05:33,850
Back then,

147
00:05:33,850 --> 00:05:34,690
Tang was famous

148
00:05:34,810 --> 00:05:35,960
for her notes.

149
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,170
Everyone would borrow them

150
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:38,900
to study and copy before exams.

151
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,270
Feng Weiran even said

152
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,080
that with a notebook

153
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,130
in her left hand

154
00:05:45,130 --> 00:05:46,370
and an exercise book in her right hand,

155
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,280
Tang looked like

156
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,100
a gangster with weapons in both hands.

157
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:50,540
Stop talking about me.

158
00:05:50,690 --> 00:05:52,560
Do you know how ridiculous it was

159
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,710
when your cousin was doing math?

160
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:56,780
He used all kinds of
functions and equations

161
00:05:56,930 --> 00:05:58,210
and wrote down every step

162
00:05:58,210 --> 00:05:59,130
only to figure out

163
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:00,660
that there were

164
00:06:00,810 --> 00:06:02,780
one point three old ladies on the bus.

165
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:06,920
How did you get the zero point three?

166
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,510
You borrowed half an old lady from me.

167
00:06:08,730 --> 00:06:09,570
Yes.

168
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:11,710
Thank you.

169
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:13,760
