196
00:07:01,290 --> 00:07:02,210
tom yum flavor,

197
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:03,250
and spicy flavor.

198
00:07:03,250 --> 00:07:04,570
There are also many dishes,

199
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:05,460
