200
00:07:05,610 --> 00:07:06,960
non-rice vermicelli,

201
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,070
beef, tripes,

202
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,420
and fish balls.

203
00:07:10,490 --> 00:07:11,340
(Looks nice.)

204
00:07:11,690 --> 00:07:13,320
(Remember to eat dumplings
at midnight.)

205
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,880
(That's the tradition
of Chinese New Year.)

206
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,930
We have dumplings.

207
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:17,830
Jiang Shiyan's mother
made some dumplings.

208
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:20,050
They're in the fridge.
I'll take them out

209
00:07:20,050 --> 00:07:20,890
