210
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:22,100
(Happy Chinese New Year.)

211
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,710
(Happy Chinese New Year, Hui.)

212
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:25,200
Happy Chinese New Year.

213
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,040
Bye.

