234
00:08:47,210 --> 00:08:48,760
The one we had
during our streaming last time.

235
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:51,850
It's in the car. There are two flavors,

236
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:52,690
tom yum

237
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,590
and spicy hotpot.

238
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,470
Bring them both here.

239
00:08:55,610 --> 00:08:56,450
Okay.

240
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:58,780
